; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;359&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile4.uf.tistory.com/image/2314424056AF70D3070AC1&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;갠적으로 이번 2016년 1월 추천애니는 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;디멘션w, 나만이 없는 거리, 하루치카, 재와 환상의 그림갈, 부부키 부란키를 꼽고 싶습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile6.uf.tistory.com/original/210C504756AF72AE3723B5&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;278&quot; width=&quot;500&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile6.uf.tistory.com/image/210C504756AF72AE3723B5&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://manggazip.tistory.com/2883&quot;&gt;2016/01/26 - Hisasi 마장학원 HxH 2016년 7월 신작애니로 방송시기 확정&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://manggazip.tistory.com/2519&quot;&gt;2015/09/26 - 마장학원 HxH 애니화 기획중?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; 지난해 애니화 기획이 진행되고 2016년 여름 신작애니로 방송 예정인 서비스 애니 마장학원 HxH PV 및 애니판 키비쥬얼 이미지가 공개되었습니다. 유튜브에 공개된 PV는 썸네일부터가 범상치 않은 작품의 정체성을 여실히 드러내고 있습니다. 1권 읽어본 저도 이 작품이 새여동생 마왕의 계약자 작품에 버금갈 정도로 눈요기가 될 것으로 예상하고 있습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Nanum Gothic&quot; color=&quot;#495f90&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;b&gt;마장학원 HxH PV 썸네일부터가 위험해!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;iframe height=&quot;360&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; allowfullscreen src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/LcFf0mI5KTQ&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; PV 동영상은 원작 라노벨 갓사시 일러 위주의 영상이군요. 접속개장이 기대되는 작품입니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; 개취로는 Hisasi씨보다 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Hamao씨 그림체를 선호하는 편입니다. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile9.uf.tistory.com/original/2372573C56AF6E4C109F8A&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;790&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile9.uf.tistory.com/image/2372573C56AF6E4C109F8A&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;티저 사이트 주소 : &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;http://www.masou-hh.com/&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;http://www.masou-hh.com/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;center&gt;


&lt;ins data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-7727649960750393&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;6066045188&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt;
&lt;/center&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;갓사시의 그림체가 워낙 펜터치 끝이 날카롭게 정리된 느낌이 덜 들어서 그런지 애니판은 좀 깔끔하고 성숙된 느낌입니다. 눈매도 원작은 색기가 감도는데 애니판은 조금 어른스러운 느낌이네요.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/original/253B5B3556AF6EA31A4C2A&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;360&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile10.uf.tistory.com/image/253B5B3556AF6EA31A4C2A&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/original/230FAF3556AF6EA3338202&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;360&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile25.uf.tistory.com/image/230FAF3556AF6EA3338202&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/original/2769133556AF6EA402E23F&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;360&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile7.uf.tistory.com/image/2769133556AF6EA402E23F&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span dir=&quot;http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/original/2253723556AF6EA50CCE7E&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;lightbox&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;360&quot; width=&quot;640&quot; src=&quot;http://cfile26.uf.tistory.com/image/2253723556AF6EA50CCE7E&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
